OL,3,CCare worker repeatedly sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted vulnerable residents at care
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FA care worker who repeatedly sexually
OL,8,Fassaulted two vulnerable residents at
OL,9,Fa care home in East Kent has been
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FStaff became concerned about David
OL,13,FJones' behaviour, and when they
OL,14,Ffollowed him to a resident's room
OL,15,Fduring a night shift, he was caught
OL,16,Facting indecently.
OL,18,FStaff reported him to police who then
OL,19,Farrested him on suspicion of engaging
OL,20,Fin sexual activity with a person
OL,21,Fwithout consent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
