OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779631868
OL,3,CCare worker repeatedly sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted vulnerable residents at care
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FDuring a search of his home, they
OL,8,Frecovered a mobile phone which was
OL,9,Ffound to contain multiple photos and
OL,10,Fvideos of a sexual nature involving a
OL,11,Fsecond victim.
OL,13,FOfficers also discovered hundreds of
OL,14,Findecent images of children.
OL,16,FThe 53-year-old was charged with
OL,17,Fmultiple sexual offences including the
OL,18,Fpossession of incident images of
OL,19,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
