PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779631868
OL,3,CCare worker repeatedly sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted vulnerable residents at care
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FHe pleaded guilty to all charges and
OL,8,Fwas sentenced to 19 years in prison.
OL,10,FDetective Sergeant Richard Allingham
OL,11,Fsaid: "Instead of fulfilling his duty
OL,12,Fof care, Jones exploited vulnerable
OL,13,Fwomen for his own sexual gratification.
OL,15,F"His actions were deplorable and a
OL,16,Fprofound breach of trust.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
